        <trans-unit id="108" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>This procedure walks you through setting up the accelerated depreciation parameters and posting profiles.</source>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="109" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>In order to complete this task, the Fixed Asset configuration key must be selected.</source>
